  "title": "Vibrant Gooey Portuguese Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A fermented and gooey Portuguese dish featuring lamb stock, perfect for curing hangovers, this satvik-friendly stew is a hearty and comforting meal. It combines the richness of lamb with the brightness of fermented ingredients.",
